snippet.title: Captain Tsubasa: Rise of New Champions - German Junior Youth Trailer - PS4/PC/SWITCH
snippet.description:
Carried by their leader Schneider, the German Junior Youth 🇩🇪 is good at both offense and defense to outshine their opponents. This top favorite team proudly marches on to victory in Captain Tsubasa: Rise of New Champions ⚽
